    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, honest condition and serves as a reliable daily driver. The exterior shows some age with minor scratches, a few small dings, and some clear coat fading on the roof, while the interior has visible wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. Mechanically, it starts up and runs consistently, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads and a suspension check to keep it at its best. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and cosmetic history.",
      "price": 21500.0,
